    Engine ID class that defines the engine ID.
    DecoderConfigValues.EngineType
    Engine Type class that defines the engine type
    DecoderConfigValues.LightsMode

    OCR Mode class that defines the mode settings

    DecoderConfigValues.SymbologyID
    Symbology ID class that defines the supported symbology IDs.
    DecodeResult
    Used to store decoded results data

    Exception result codes for all functions.
    DecodeWindowing
    Used for configuring a Decode Window
    DecodeWindowing.DecodeWindow
    Decode Window coordinate settings.
    DecodeWindowing.DecodeWindowLimits
    Decode Window Min/Max Limits that are allowed to be specified.
    DecodeWindowing.DecodeWindowMode
    Decode Window Mode setting.
    DecodeWindowing.DecodeWindowShowWindow
    Show Decode Window setting to ensure the appropriate window is being set for application (for debug purposes).
    ExposureValues  
    ExposureValues.ConformImage
    ConformImage class that defines whether or not the image should conform to exposure settings.
    ExposureValues.ExposureMethod 已过时

    ExposureMode class that defines the exposure mode that will be used during image capture.

    ImageAttributes
